Description:
Annotation on the envelope: "Mantua - Abresch Zu den Selbst-bildnissen von Rubens"

- Subfolder (Annotation: "Rubens zu den Selbstbildnissen"):
    - Extracts from different publications about Rubens' self-portraits
- Reproductions of Rubens' self-portraits and 'Rubens, Helene Fourment and their son Frans in the Garden'
- Extracts from different publications
- Bibliographic references
- Transcriptions of letters written by Burchard to Mr. Abresch
- Essay: 'Zu den Selbstbildnissen und Bildnissen von Rubens' by Evers, in "Jahrbuch der preussischen Kunstsammlungen", 1943
 
  
Loose documentation reunited with the folder:   
     
- Photo of Rubens' portrait  
  
Loose documentation in the Rubensdocumentation of the Rubenianum:  
        
- Photo of a Rubens self-portrait engraving (Rubenianum "Evers 1993" stamp on the back)
- Photo of the detail of Helene's dress
